{"tid":2162079,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇稱政府應延長限聚措施 若放寬會令病毒重新傳播","createTime":"2020-08-18T02:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T04:03:24.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36ea45904b465b7e720b7af235699ce40713207e","tid":2162079,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"袁國勇稱政府應延長限聚措施 若放寬會令病毒重新傳播<br />\n2020-08-18 HKT 09:55<br />\n<br />\n&quot;政府再延長禁晚市堂食及二人限聚令等措施一星期，至本月25日。政府專家顧問、港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇認為，政府應該再延長限聚措施，又說現時每日的確診個案仍維持在40至70宗之間，各區都有個案，如果現時放寬措施，會令病毒再重新開始傳播，是自找麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>被問到何時可以放寬晚市堂食，他認為個案數目要回落到單位數</strong></span>。他說病毒有機會在短距離間有空氣傳播，所有會除口罩的地點都是高危控制點，在重開食肆前要先有措施應對，例如增加食肆內的空氣流動速度，將空氣過濾或消毒等......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544301-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544301-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF85qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=170f142a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544301-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=207f21a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544301-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">連登恐懼撚會認為個案數目應該跌至0才可放寬晚市堂食</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5414c7dcd169b581f4652d2f9be52ffd0ee54f40","tid":2162079,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n支持個案數目應該跌至0才可放寬晚市堂食的請正評"}]}